        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You briefly transform your features into the horrific visage of a hag, striking fear into your enemies. Foes in the area must attempt a Will save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The foe is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The foe is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The foe is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (5th)</strong> Foes in the area are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1} on a success, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2} on a failure, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 3} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fleeing]{Fleeing} for 1 round on a critical failure. They are still unaffected on a critical success.</p>"
